---
import ponceuse from '~/assets/images/ponceuse.png';
import secheMain from '~/assets/images/seche_main.png';
import vernis from '~/assets/images/vernis.png';
import produits from '~/assets/images/produits.png';
import mains from '~/assets/images/mains.png';
import bain from '~/assets/images/bain.png';
---

<div class="salon-content">

  <div class="salon-photos">
    <img src="/images/salon1.jpg" alt="Espace manucure Joanails" class="salon-photo" loading="lazy" />
    <img src="/images/salon2.jpg" alt="Espace détente Joanails" class="salon-photo" loading="lazy" />
  </div>

  <p class="salon-intro">C'est avec grand plaisir que je prendrai soin de vos mains et de vos pieds !</p>

  <div class="salon-features">
    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <img src={ponceuse.src} alt="" class="illus" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-title">À proximité de tout</span>
        <span class="feature-desc">Un cocon de beauté proche du centre-ville de Cherbourg.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <img src={vernis.src} alt="" class="illus" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-title">Équipé et moderne</span>
        <span class="feature-desc">Tous les équipements pour sublimer vos mains et vos pieds.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <img src={secheMain.src} alt="" class="illus" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-title">Pour tous les goûts</span>
        <span class="feature-desc">De la couleur classique aux strass, paillettes et nail art sur mesure.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <img src={mains.src} alt="" class="illus" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-title">Confort optimal</span>
        <span class="feature-desc">Un espace cocooning dédié au bien-être de vos mains et vos pieds.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <img src={produits.src} alt="" class="illus" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-title">Ambiance florale</span>
        <span class="feature-desc">Un décor chaleureux aux touches délicates et fleuries.</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="feature-card">
      <div class="feature-icon">
        <img src={bain.src} alt="" class="illus" aria-hidden="true" />
      </div>
      <div class="feature-text">
        <span class="feature-title">Beauté sur mesure</span>
        <span class="feature-desc">Chaque prestation est adaptée à vos envies et vos besoins.</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</div>

<style>
  .salon-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1.25rem;
  }

  .salon-photos {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }
  .salon-photo {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 4/3;
    object-fit: cover;
    border-radius: 14px;
  }

  .salon-intro {
    font-family: var(--aw-font-heading);
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: rgb(80, 48, 28);
    text-align: center;
    margin: 0;
    line-height: 1.45;
    padding: 0 0.25rem;
  }

  .salon-features {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.625rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.875rem;
    background: rgba(231, 193, 155, 0.18);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 0.875rem 1rem;
  }

  .feature-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 52px;
    height: 52px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
  }
  .illus {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: sepia(0.3) saturate(1.2);
  }

  .feature-text {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }
  .feature-title {
    font-family: var(--aw-font-heading);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: rgb(80, 48, 28);
  }
  .feature-desc {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    line-height: 1.55;
    color: rgb(91, 75, 64);
  }
</style>
